<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your ATC Africa Account Credentials</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1f1f1f;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f6f7f9;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 28px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #e6e7eb;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        padding-bottom: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #4b0082;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .welcome-message {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #566074;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .credentials-box {
        background-color: #f7f8fc;
        border: 1px solid #eceef2;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .credential-item {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .credential-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f1f1f;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .credential-value {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 10px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #4b0082;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .important-notice {
        background-color: #fff8e5;
        border: 1px solid #f4e2b6;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .important-notice h3 {
        color: #6a4e00;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .important-notice p {
        color: #6a4e00;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background-color: #4b0082;
        color: #ffffff !important;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #3e006e;
      }
      .btn-secondary {
        background-color: #566074;
        color: #ffffff !important;
      }
      .btn-secondary:hover {
        background-color: #434b5a;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding-top: 16px;
        border-top: 1px solid #eceef2;
        color: #566074;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .security-tips {
        background-color: #f7f8fc;
        border: 1px solid #eceef2;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      .security-tips h3 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .security-tips ul {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">ATC Africa</div>
        <div class="welcome-message">Welcome to ATC Africa!</div>
      </div>

      <p>Hello <strong><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></strong>,</p>

      <p>
        Your account has been created successfully by an administrator. Below
        are your login credentials:
      </p>

      <div class="credentials-box">
        <div class="credential-item">
          <div class="credential-label">Email Address:</div>
          <div class="credential-value"><%= email %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="credential-item">
          <div class="credential-label">Temporary Password:</div>
          <div class="credential-value"><%= temporaryPassword %></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="important-notice">
        <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice</h3>
        <p>
          For your security, you <strong>must</strong> change this temporary
          password immediately after your first login. This temporary password
          will expire and you will be required to set a new, secure password.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="btn btn-primary"
          >Login to Your Account</a
        >
        <a href="<%= changePasswordUrl %>" class="btn btn-secondary"
          >Change Password</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="security-tips">
        <h3>üîí Security Tips</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Change your password immediately after first login</li>
          <li>Use a strong password with at least 8 characters</li>
          <li>Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters</li>
          <li>Never share your login credentials with anyone</li>
          <li>Log out from shared or public computers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support
        team.
      </p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        <strong>ATC Africa Team</strong>
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>
          ¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ATC Africa. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
